CSS3 on Home Page

For this lesson, I added the following Twitter Bootstrap Customize features to my home page:

1) Pill-style menu for my class projects

2) Grid-based menu for my list of class projects

3) A carousel-style slideshow with photos of my children

4) My introduction

5) My goals for this class

6) A plan for my Final Project.

Here is the HTML code for my home page:

